Class FluentHelperModification<FluentHelperT,EntityT,ResultT>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    FluentHelperT - The fluent helper type.
    EntityT - The type of the entity this OData request operates on, if any.

    All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Beta
public abstract class FluentHelperModification<FluentHelperT,EntityT,ResultT>
extends FluentHelperBasic<FluentHelperT,EntityT,ResultT>
    Representation of an OData modification request (Create, Update, Delete) as a fluent interface for further configuring the request and executing it.
